OL,3,CFour Midlands MPs brought in to sure
OL,4,Cup PM's government after resignations
OL,6,FFour Midlands MPs have been rewarded
OL,7,Ffor their loyalty to Keir Starmer with
OL,8,Fjobs in his government, as he is
OL,9,Ffighting to stay in Number 10.
OL,11,FMP for Bolsover Natalie Fleet has
OL,12,Fbecome a junior minister in the Home
OL,13,FOffice, while Derby North MP Catherine
OL,14,FAtkinson has been made a junior
OL,15,Fminister in the Ministry of Justice.
OL,17,FBirmingham Edgbaston MP Preet Gill
OL,18,Fwill become a junior minister in the
OL,19,FDepartment of Health, and Telford MP
OL,20,FShaun Davies an Assistant Whip.
