OL,3,CFour Midlands MPs brought in to sure
OL,4,Cup PM's government after resignations
OL,6,FThis comes after a number of
OL,7,Fresignations yesterday, including high-
OL,8,Fprofile minister and Birmingham
OL,9,FYardley MP Jess Phillips.
OL,11,FShe resigned as safeguarding minister,
OL,12,Fsaying she believed Sir Keir Starmer
OL,13,Fwas a "good man" but that "is not
OL,14,Fenough".
OL,26,@uD@GOUuD@PO]vD@GO]
