OL,3,CFour Midlands MPs brought in to sure
OL,4,Cup PM's government after resignations
OL,6,FIn her resignation letter, Ms Phillips
OL,7,Fsaid: "I want to start by first saying
OL,8,Fthat we have worked closely together
OL,9,Fon Violence Against Women and Girls
OL,10,Ffor many years, and I have no doubt
OL,11,Fyou have genuine knowledge and desire
OL,12,Fto rectify this dreadful social ill.
OL,13,FWe have started to make steps towards
OL,14,Fchange whilst in government and I have
OL,15,Fbeen grateful for your support.
OL,26,@oD@GOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,377,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F376A1778850694
OL,3,CFour Midlands MPs brought in to sure
OL,4,Cup PM's government after resignations
OL,6,F"However, it would be remiss of me not
OL,7,Fto say that real change and direction
OL,8,Fin this area usually came from threats
OL,9,Fmade by me in light of catastrophic
OL,10,Fmistakes. The Mandelson saga, whenever
OL,11,Fit bubbled up, made Number 10 kick
OL,12,Finto gear on the subject in order to
OL,13,Fprove our credentials. I will never
OL,14,Fwaste a crisis to make advancements
OL,15,Ffor women and girls, and so demands
OL,16,Fwere made, and some were met.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/5
